com.puppycrawl.tools.checkstyle.grammars.javadoc

Interface JavadocParserListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavadocParserBaseListener

    public interface JavadocParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by JavadocParser.
